data.description: Beautifully renovated, move-in ready home! Welcome to 837 Silver Oak Drive, a cozy 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offering 1,464 SF. This home sits on 1.05 acres with a gorgeous covered patio off the front of the home that has an amazing view of the Ruby Mountains! Upon entering you'll see an open floor plan with a newly renovated kitchen. As you walk through the home you'll notice all new flooring throughout and new vanities in both of the bathrooms! The wood burning stove in the living room is perfect for keeping you warm on chilly winter evenings! Step outside to a partially fenced in backyard, with a chicken coop, wood storage, and a fenced in garden just a short walk from the chicken coop! The trampoline in the backyard will also stay
